CompanyDescription.label: Company Description
CompanyDescription.value: Senseonics Holdings Inc is a medical technology company. It is focused on the design, development, and commercialization of the glucose monitoring system, which helps people to manage their diabetes. Its products and services include Continuous glucose monitoring system, Sensor, Smart transmitter, and Mobile app. The firm has a Glucose monitoring product segment. The majority of the revenue is generated outside of the United States.
